reviewText: I purchased this volume as well as the other 3 and I highly recommend you do the same as I found that all the discs were mislabeled and arranged. (Disc 2 from Volume 3 in the Volume 1 case, etc.) Overall, I am happy; just a little stressed of making sure everything was in the right case according to the episodes.
Urban Legends, Just like we remember. It has scary stories that will make you jump. I miss seeing it on TV.
